#######################################
######### ExternalName Service ##########
Used when application needs external dependency.

@@ Example:
Application
     ⬇︎
Database Outside Kubernetes

@@ Create:

apiVersion: v1
kind: Service
metadata:
  name: mysql-external
spec:
  type: ExternalName
  externalName: mysql.company.com

Now Pods can use mysql-external instead of remembering FQDN.

#####################################
####### Service Types Summary #######
Type	        Internal    	External
ClusterIP        Yes                No
NodePort	     Yes               Yes
LoadBalancer	 Yes	           Yes
ExternalName	External Resource	Yes

